<details><summary>Simplify the Google Sheets import</summary>

___

**The suggestion recommends simplifying the Google Sheets import feature by <br>removing the fragile DOM-scraping implementation. It advocates for keeping only <br>the more robust clipboard-based and API-driven approach to reduce redundancy and <br>future maintenance.**


### Examples:



<details>
<summary>
<a href="https://github.com/kokayicobb/consuelo_on_call_coaching/pull/788/files#diff-83a5de54280e1a04c78c3389c2be44c8b73ccf88fdf5d9cf883d13c6a07bceeeR1-R1093">consuelo-extension/src/entrypoints/content/sheets.ts [1-1093]</a>
</summary></details>



