<a href="https://github.com/kokayicobb/consuelo_on_call_coaching/pull/788/files#diff-a3ec9f02db0621d97995424e4c9d693d3d467704903cc35b33e1896555d5c352R1-R762">consuelo-extension/src/entrypoints/content-sheets.ts [1-762]</a>
</summary></details>




### Solution Walkthrough:



#### Before:
