<details><summary>Properly cancel in-flight search requests</summary>

___

**Fix the search cancellation logic by creating a new <code>AbortController</code> for each <br>search and passing its signal to the <code>searchContacts</code> API call.**

[consuelo-extension/src/hooks/useContacts.ts [95-109]](https://github.com/kokayicobb/consuelo_on_call_coaching/pull/788/files#diff-dbc8cc47b0c521274a5dad1ac8a554ac31cfca6428cb92a04ade8c429acf0fa3R95-R109)

